item.title: No title
item.description: I struggle a lot with controlling my impulses. And I often end up doing things that seem really stupid or unnecessary when I look back on it. I buy stuff I donâ€™t need, eat tons of unhealthy food, waste hours browsing news sites, YouTube, or other sites filled with brainless entertainment. And I very often end up avoiding the things I had planned to do if I feel that they are too hard. And I have been trying hard lately to understand why I behave this way. I have even gone to see a shrink a few time, in order to find some logic to what is going on in my head.
